# Rust build artifacts
/target/
**/*.rs.bk

# Cargo lock is committed for binaries
# Cargo.lock  # uncomment if this becomes a library-only crate

# ragent CARGO_TARGET_DIR isolation
# When ragent runs shell commands that invoke cargo, it sets CARGO_TARGET_DIR
# to avoid Windows MAX_PATH issues. If the temp dir resolves to a relative path
# (e.g. in some CI environments), the artifacts may land here.
*ragent-target/
Temp*/

